>>>>>>> # Diabetes specialist nurses: join our consultative group
>>>>>>> Diabetes UK would like to build a group of Diabetes Specialist Nurses
(DSNs) and Nurse Consultants who are able to feed into the charity's work
through consultation and provide intelligence from the front-line of nursing.
We'd like to work with DSNs to drive up standards of diabetes care, and to
>>>>>>> As a member of the DSN Consultative Group, you will receive a monthly
e-newsletter featuring new developments in diabetes care, examples of best
practice and information about how Diabetes UK can support you as a DSN.
